==English==

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|belong||}}

#To have its proper place.
#:''Where does this document '''belong'''?''
#(''of a person'') To be accepted in a group.
#:''You don't '''belong''' here &mdash; get out.''
#(''followed by'' '''to''') To be the property of.
#:''That house '''belongs''' to me.''
#(''followed by'' '''to''') To be the guardian, spouse or partner of.
#{{settheory}} (''followed by'' '''to''') To be an [[element]] of (a set).

====Derived terms====
*[[belonging]]

